<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="service-n">service <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'sɜːvɪs/    美 /'sɜːrvɪs/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>公共服务系统；公共事业机构：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the Civil Service Examination 
公务员考试</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the <strong>National Health Service</strong> (the NHS) 
(英国的)国民保健制度</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>服务；效力；使用：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>service industry</strong> / <strong>charge</strong> 
服务业/服务费</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>In 1291, after 17 <strong>years of service</strong> to the Emperor, Marco returned to Italy.  
1291年，在为皇帝效力了17年之后，马可·波罗回到了意大利。</p><footer>北师大③-8</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Sorry, the number you dialed is <strong>out of service</strong>. 
对不起，您拨打的号码已停机。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="at-sbs-service">at sb’s service</h3>
<p>1.<strong>听候某人吩咐；为某人效劳：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Just feel free to call Room Service. We’re always at your service. 
请尽管呼叫服务部，我们随时为您服务。</p></div>

<h3 id="pay-lip-service-to">pay lip service (to)</h3>
<p>1.<strong>对…空口答应 (而不行动)：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Should we just pay lip service or take practical measures to protect the environment?  
我们应该仅仅只是说说而已还是应该采取实际行动去保护环境呢？</p><footer>2013 江苏改</footer></div>

<h3 id="service-area-station">service area / station</h3>
<p>1.<strong>(高速公路旁的) 服务区 / 服务站</strong>  </p></div>